'''菲利港'''（Port Fairy，{{IPAc-en|p|ɔː|t|_|ˈ|f|ɛər|i}}<ref>{{cite book |editor-last=Butler |editor-first=S. |title=[[Macquarie_Dictionary|Macquarie Dictionary]] |edition=5th |contribution=Port Fairy |contribution-url=http://www.macquariedictionary.com.au |year=2009 |publisher=Macquarie Dictionary Publishers Pty Ltd |location=Sydney |isbn=978-18-7642-966-9 }}</ref>）是[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]][[維多利亞州|維多利亞州]]西南部的遺憾海岸小鎮，位於[[墨爾本|墨爾本]]以西{{convert|290|km}}，[[瓦南布爾|瓦南布爾]]以西{{convert|28|km|mi|0}}。菲利港這個名字首次見於記載是在1828年<ref>{{Citation  | last =  | title = Portland Bay Extracts  | newspaper = The Sydney Morning Herald  | page = 4  | date = 23 March 1843  | url = http://trove.nla.gov.au/ndp/del/article/12415565  | accessdate = 13 February 2011}}, quoting the Portland Mercury</ref>。這裡的主要產業是旅遊業。
